NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|There is also a slight modification to DONT that some people play. Some people play 2H is a single suited heart hand. If they play that, then Eileen would bid 2H which is slightly more informative and preemptive. Also if you play that, then with spades and hearts, you have to double and then bid 2H. That variation is more complicated and I recommend you stick to the original version but make sure you use it aggressively.|
